Write Java programs for the following:

01. Write a program to print whether a number is even or odd, also take input from the user.
02. Take name as input and print a greeting message for that particular name.
03. Write a program to input principal, time, and rate (P, T, R) from the user and find Simple Interest.
04. Take in two numbers and an operator (+, -, *, /) and calculate the value. (Use if conditions)
05. Take 2 numbers as input and print the largest number.
06. Input currency in rupees and output in USD.
07. To calculate Fibonacci Series up to n numbers.
08. To find out whether the given String is Palindrome or not.
09. To find Armstrong Number between two given number.